# 📁 Collection: group 


## End-point: group/submit
### Method: GET
>```
>http://localhost:8080/api/group/submit
>```
### Body (**raw**)

```json
{
  "name": "Group2 of user 8",
  "description": "only the one can pass",
  "privacy": "public",
  "invited": ""
}
```

## End-point: user/register
### Method: GET
>```
>http://localhost:8000/api/user/register
>```
### Body (**raw**)

```json
{
  "email": "sagar@sagar.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "firstName": "sagar",
  "lastName": "yadav",
  "dob": "10/05/1983",
  "avatar": "",
  "nickname": "sagarnick",
  "aboutMe": "I belive in Jesus the saviour",
  "public": true
}
```

### Response: 200
```json
{
    "UUID": "da2c0663-25a1-405a-8f33-e1cd8bfbe7d9",
    "username": "sagarnick"
}
```
